- UH, YEAH.

82
00:05:15,291 --> 00:05:17,541
CAN I WARM UP YOUR
BENTO BOX FOR YOU?

83
00:05:18,125 --> 00:05:19,375
- HUH?

84
00:05:19,458 --> 00:05:22,416
- DO YOU NEED CHOPSTICKS
OR A LASER GUN?

85
00:05:22,500 --> 00:05:24,125
- SO IT DOESN'T MAKE
ANY SENSE,

86
00:05:24,208 --> 00:05:26,458
BUT I SUDDENLY HAVE THIS
STRONG, INTENSE,

87
00:05:26,541 --> 00:05:29,458
HOWEVER, RANDOM, NEED TO LET
SLEEPY PANTS BE MY PRINCE.

88
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:32,791
