WHAT YOU MEAN NOW

89
00:05:32,875 --> 00:05:33,958
ABOUT THE TWO LINES IN
THE WORD "PERSON"

90
00:05:34,041 --> 00:05:35,333
LEANING ON EACH
OTHER FOR SUPPORT

91
