102
00:05:58,500 --> 00:06:00,041
WE'RE GONNA HAVE TO HAVE A TALK.

103
00:06:01,291 --> 00:06:02,875
OH, HE LEFT HIS I.D. HERE.

104
00:06:04,708 --> 00:06:06,458
KEITA TSUWABUKI, HUH?

105
00:06:06,541 --> 00:06:09,250
AND WHAT A COINCIDENCE. HE LIVES
RIGHT DOWN THE STREET FROM ME.

106
00:06:10,541 --> 00:06:11,708
