107
00:06:13,375 --> 00:06:15,458
- WHAT A KIND PERSON
YOU ARE TO DROP THIS OFF.

108
00:06:15,541 --> 00:06:17,791
- SHE'S NOT ONLY BEAUTIFUL,
SHE'S THOUGHTFUL, TOO.

109
00:06:17,875 --> 00:06:19,875
- WHY DON'T YOU STAY
AND HAVE DINNER WITH US?

110
00:06:19,958 --> 00:06:22,416
- OUR SON'S SO LUCKY
TO HAVE MET AN ANGEL LIKE YOU.

111
