118
00:06:39,916 --> 00:06:41,458
- THIS CAN'T BE THE
RIGHT ADDRESS.

119
00:06:41,541 --> 00:06:43,375
NO ONE WOULD CHOOSE
TO LIVE HERE.

120
00:06:43,458 --> 00:06:46,166
I CAN FEEL MY FACE BREAKING OUT
JUST LOOKING AT IT.

121
00:06:46,250 --> 00:06:47,416
- HELP YOU FIND SOMETHING?

122
00:06:47,500 --> 00:06:49,541
- ( gasps )
- OKAY, THIS IS WEIRD.

123
00:06:49,625 --> 00:06:51,666
- AREN'T YOU THAT TIGHTWAD CHICK
FROM MY CLASS?

124
00:06:51,750 --> 00:06:53,000
WHAT WAS YOUR NAME AGAIN?

125
00:06:53,083 --> 00:06:55,833
STARTED WITH A 'K', DIDN'T IT?
OR WAS IT A "C".

126
00:06:55,916 --> 00:06:58,375
- NO! IT'S ICHIKO SAKURA.

127
00:06:58,458 --> 00:07:00,625
SO, YEAH, I FOUND THIS
BY YOUR DESK BEFORE I LEFT.

128
00:07:00,708 --> 00:07:02,208
TSUWABUKI, RIGHT?

129
00:07:02,291 --> 00:07:05,458
- YEAH, YOU CAME ALL THE WAY OUT
HERE JUST TO RETURN THIS TO ME?

130
00:07:05,541 --> 00:07:07,250
THANK YOU. THAT'S SO...

131
00:07:07,333 --> 00:07:09,583
- SELFLESS AND GOOD
SAMARITAN-LY? I KNOW, RIGHT?

132
00:07:09,666 --> 00:07:11,625
- YEAH. SO, I GUESS
I SHOULD DO SOMETHING

133
00:07:11,708 --> 00:07:14,208
