00:07:20,041 --> 00:07:22,375
HE'S HOT AND WE'RE CLEARLY
ABOUT TO FALL IN LOVE.

138
00:07:24,041 --> 00:07:25,333
- HOW'S IT GOING, GUYS?

139
00:07:25,416 --> 00:07:27,041
- Mika: YAY, YOU'RE BACK.
- Rika: WELCOME HOME.

140
00:07:27,125 --> 00:07:29,250
- WHOA, IS THAT YOUR
NEW GIRLFRIEND, KEITA?

141
00:07:29,333 --> 00:07:30,541
SHE'S SO PRETTY.

142
00:07:30,625 --> 00:07:32,958
- HI, KEITA'S GIRLFRIEND.
DO YOU PLAY D AND D?

143
00:07:33,041 --> 00:07:36,458
- UM. WE'RE HAPPY
TO HAVE YOU. WELCOME.

144
00:07:36,541 --> 00:07:38,791
- WHAT THE HELL? HOW
MANY PEOPLE LIVE HERE?

145
00:07:38,875 --> 00:07:41,958
- THAT TOOK FOREVER. HOW FAR DID
YOU HAVE TO GO TO GET SOY SAUCE?

146
00:07:42,041 --> 00:07:44,583
- FELT LIKE EGYPT, BUT THEY WERE
SELLING IT CHEAP AT THE MARKET.

147
00:07:45,583 --> 00:07:46,750
- ( chuckles awkwardly )

148
00:07:47,791 --> 00:07:50,458
- All: THANK YOU FOR THE FOOD.

149
00:07:50,541 --> 00:07:53,208
- RYUTA, I SAW THAT.
YOU JUST GRABBED THREE PICKLES.

150
00:07:53,291 --> 00:07:55,333
- WE'RE ONLY SUPPOSED
TO GET TWO. NO FAIR.

151
00:07:55,416 --> 00:07:58,125
