208
00:10:04,541 --> 00:10:05,666
FOR ALL TWENTY OF YOU.

209
00:10:05,750 --> 00:10:08,708
AND YOU COULD AFFORD
BETTER FOOD. AM I RIGHT?

210
00:10:08,791 --> 00:10:10,083
- ALL RIGHT, THAT'S IT.

211
00:10:10,166 --> 00:10:12,083
YOU'VE GOTTA BE THE RUDEST
PERSON I'VE EVER MET.

212
00:10:12,166 --> 00:10:15,458
WHAT ARE YOU SO ANGRY ABOUT?
OR ARE YOU SOME KIND OF PSYCHO?

213
00:10:15,541 --> 00:10:16,875
